description.text: Great location that's close to everything! Comfortable, well-maintained mid-City home has 3 bedroom and 2 bathrooms with many upgrades. Lots of natural light. Living room with fireplace and dining area. Hardwood floors throughout. Primary bedroom suite with full bathroom. Laundry in service porch. High efficiency AC/Heating split units in living room and each bedroom. New window shutters throughout house. Private back yard with new artificial turf. The garage is set is up as additional outdoor living space makes it a great area for entertaining. Large storage shed included! Close to Culver City, the Culver City Arts District, USC, Silicon Beach , and Metro Expo Line stations where you can go east to Downtown Los Angeles or west to the beach.

Newly constructed in 2018, this elegant townhome is situated on the palm-tree lined Palm Grove Avenue. Bathed in abundant natural sunlight, this spacious dwelling boasts four bedrooms and four bathrooms. Inside, you'll find beautiful hardwood floors, recessed lighting, and a central air and heating system. The contemporary kitchen showcases Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, modern fixtures, a gas stove, and ample cabinet space. Further amenities include a convenient in-unit washer and dryer, two en-suite bedrooms, double pane windows, and a private two-car garage. Perfectly situated, this residence enjoys a prime location with easy access to Downtown Culver City, as well as renowned eateries and cafes like Mizlala, Alta, and Adams Wine Bar. Nearby, you'll find farmers markets, Sprouts, Target, and convenient transportation options, including easy access to the 10 Freeway. Photos are representative of the neighboring unit with comparable updates & finishes.

Totally Renovated Modern Gated 2 Story Duplex With 2 Bedrooms and 1 Baths each. Kitchen with Shaker White Cabinets and Ceasarstone Countertops, Dishwasher and Stainless Steel Appliances. Upper Unit with Balcony off the Living-room. Large Closets with Glass Panel Doors, Bathrooms with Lighted Bluetooth Mirrors. Off Street Parking, Close to Metro Link, Shopping and Public Transportation.

description.text: Beautifully remodeled 2 bedroom 1 bathroom back house for rent in the western part of the fast changing West Adams neighborhood. Within close distance to the new Whole Foods, Culver City and restaurants on Adams Blvd. This unit features hardwood flooring, stainless steel appliances and an in unit washer and dryer. One unique thing about this unit, is it features a private yard that is only accessible to this back house. Pets are welcomed, max is 2 with additional deposit. No monthly pet rent. Application fee is a none refundable: $55 per applicant. 12 month lease Apply at TurboTenant: Property Id 1195887

description.name: K.I.G. Property Management
description.text: (888) 270-4452 - (RLNE7237519) New Construction! Modern 3 Bedroom Luxury Townhome with Parking and W/D In-Unit! - Brand new apartment constructed in 2020 near Culver City. Very close to downtown Culver, major highways and transit. A reasonable drive away from both Santa Monica and downtown LA! Please note this unit will be available in June 2023. The spacious apartment has 3 bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms, plus a shared guest half bath in the main living room. Lots of light and windows throughout. Brand new kitchen with quartz counter tops and new stainless steel appliances. In-unit washer and dryers; heating and A/C in-unit. A 1-car garage and 1 additional parking spot included. Private balcony! 2104 Hauser Blvd is a sleek, impressively constructed 2020 fourplex 5 minutes from Culver City and the countless local hotspots and conveniences in the area, including the trendy Helms Bakery District! This neighborhood is rapidly becoming the hottest rental market in Los Angeles, with several of the most highly anticipated mixed-use developments coming in within 8 SHORT MINUTES of this property: the Culver City Steps (Amazon Studios headquarters), Ivy Station (HBO headquarters), and the Cumulus development. With the influx of entertainment, tech and creative jobs coming to town. Follow up with KIG for tour information, an Online Application and Renter's Qualifications! *Deposit Only on approved credit* Qualifications include that household must qualify by proving 2.5X of combined income, 640 or higher credit scores, No evictions or landlord collections, and can pass a criminal background check. Must be an adult over 18 years old to apply. The Application fee is $40 each. 2104 Hauser is a single-family townhome located in the fourplex property in West Adams/Mid Wilshire neighborhood in Los Angeles County, CA the 90016 ZIP Code KIG Capital Broker License: 01904356

description.name: Kingston Management Group Inc
description.text: (310) 362-3491 - (RLNE8083958) Prime Location - Mid City 90016 - 2 bedroom w Charm & Accepting LA City Section 8 Vouchers - Tons of Charm in this freshly painted 2 bedroom unit located on Ridgeley in Los Angeles, 90016 Laminate Flooring Ceiling Fans Gorgeous windows with a ton of natural light Accepting LA City Vouchers and **** owner will request the max rent for all voucher holders/3rd Party Programs Don't Delay - Contact Derek at 310.710.9361 to schedule a viewing.

Remodeled huge first floor unit in Spanish style residential Quadruplex. This unit gets an abundance of natural light & has a special ambiance from mature landscaping at front window. It features a highly desirable open floor plan, seamlessly integrating the kitchen, dining and living room. Entirely renovated including, new modern style kitchen with Mocha shaker cabinetry, Quartz counter tops, stainless steel appliances, recessed lighting, spacious bathroom with 48 inch vanity. Recent upgrades include, original refinished hardwood floors, chrome faucets & fixtures, inside stack-able laundry, new HVAC and more. Vaulted 9FT ceilings plus front & rear exits. Common area features surveillance, mature landscaping and an ever so charming shared back-yard. Central Mid-City location just minutes to Culver City, Beverly Hills, Down-Town LA, West Hollywood and all West-side surrounding areas.

DON'T MISS This ART DECO Community with MODERN conveniences. Centrally located, this light, bright and beautifully renovated large 2 bed/1 bath unit in historic Village Green, can be your next home. An open plan living/dining room has beautiful parquet wood floors throughout. A crisp, renovated kitchen with quarts countertops has stainless steel appliances and a easy breakfast bar. The unit has a large main bedroom with ample storage throughout. The 2nd bedroom can double as your home office. The bathroom has a beautiful vanity and glass enclosed shower/tub combo. A quick walk to the Metro Line and a short distance to major freeways, the beach, downtown and LAX. The parklike atmosphere of the grounds also offers summer concerts, movie nights and so much to enjoy. All that is second only to your own PRIVATE patio for outdoor entertaining and al fresco dining. This is a no smoking complex, not even on the patio. The unit is equip with a/c and a single car garage for parking. Guest parking is near by as well. PROPERTY AVAIL MID-JUNE.

Spectacular Location! 2 Bedroom 1.5 bath Condo, light and bright top floor unit with only 1 shared wall, in a beautifully lush, gated community surrounded by the edges of Culver City. This unit is located toward the rear of the community adding quiet enjoyment. It has a private 1 car garage as well as private community street parking for additional vehicles, In-unit stackable laundry as well as onsite laundry facility, Upgraded Kitchen and Bath, Quartz countertops, Central Heating, Portable AC Unit & Window AC units, Pet friendly! A convenient private back door off the kitchen leads to a shared balcony, quiet green space and access to the 1-car garage. The Cameo Woods complex features 24 hour security, fully gated complex, heated swimming pool, 2 Jacuzzi's, community club house, tennis courts, community garden and a dog park. The location is perfect with walking distance to Shopping centers, Whole Foods Market, Target, UCLA IDEAS Campus, Baldwin Hills Scenic Overlook, Culver City Stairs, Culver City Park, Bike Path, Hayden Tract and the Kenneth Hahn State Recreation Park. Walk to the Metro Expo Line for convenient access to Santa Monica, Westwood, Century City and Downtown LA. Couldn't be a better location for outdoor or hiking enthusiasts. Near LAX. Available July 1st. Water, Trash and Landscaping included. Property Managed by Responsible Landlord/Owner. No Monthly Management Fees. Background/Credit Check Required. Call to view today!

- (RLNE6592963) - Unique property in the heart of Los Angeles, located between the trendy Mid-City and West Adams neighborhoods. Privately owned and lovingly cared for 1924 Spanish home, recently renovated and fully modernized. Light and airy living room with vaulted ceilings. Master bedroom with ensuite bathroom and walk-in closet, plus two secondary bedrooms and additional bathroom.
